CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 12, 1956, pg. A30, reads: "Men Win! - Winning prizes in the men's division of hair styling at the Beauticians Trade Show were Lee Dorris, right, first, and Eddie Tyler, second winner. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Edward "Mitten" Tyler and Lee Dorris wearing conked hairstyles at Beauticians Trade Show, Fort Pitt Hotel
